title: Giants take advantage of Cowboys' mistakes, win 27-20
text:
> Top News Giants take advantage of Cowboys' mistakes, win 27-20 Dallas Cowboys head coach Jason Garrett, right, shakes hands with New York Giants head coach Tom Coughlin, after an NFL football game Sunday, Oct. 25, 2015, in East Rutherford, N.J. N.J. The Giants won 27-20.(AP Photo/Kathy Willens)
